---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Empowering Organizations to Unlock Their Full Potential</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        In today's fast-paced digital landscape, SynergyFlow aims to deliver
        cutting-edge solutions that leverage the power of AI to streamline your
        workflows and drive transformative results. This isn't about incremental
        improvement &mdash; it's about fundamental transformation.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose SynergyFlow?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Our comprehensive platform offers a robust suite of tools designed to elevate every facet of your business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Streamlined Workflows</h3>
          <p>
            Our robust platform seamlessly integrates with your existing tools &mdash;
            providing actionable insights that seek to elevate your team's productivity.
            Not theoretical. Practical.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary card-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Intelligent Analytics</h3>
          <p>
            Delve into comprehensive data visualizations that provide a nuanced
            understanding of your business landscape. It's not just analytics &mdash;
            it's transformation.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary card-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Enterprise Security</h3>
          <p>
            The foundation: world-class security infrastructure that leverages
            industry-leading encryption protocols to safeguard your most sensitive data.
            It's not just protection &mdash; it's peace of mind.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary card-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title">What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Don't just take our word for it &mdash; hear from the organizations we've empowered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>
            &ldquo;SynergyFlow has been a game-changer for our organization. It's not
            a product &mdash; it's a philosophy. I love using it.
            I find new capabilities every day. I try to leverage every feature.
            I can't imagine working without it. You really need to try it if you want
            to optimize your workflow.&rdquo;
          </p>
          <cite>&mdash; Sarah Johnson, Head of Innovation</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>
            &ldquo;I've been passionate about digital transformation for years. I seek
            to streamline everything. I aim to optimize every process. SynergyFlow
            makes this journey possible &mdash; it's not just a tool, it's a
            partner in your quest for operational excellence.&rdquo;
          </p>
          <cite>&mdash; Mark Thompson, Chief Synergy Officer</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="section text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Revolutionize Your Workflow?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Join thousands of forward-thinking organizations that are already leveraging
        SynergyFlow's cutting-edge platform to drive meaningful results. The question
        isn't whether to transform &mdash; it's how fast you can start.
      </p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
  }

  .testimonials {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .testimonial {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .testimonial p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
